      "notes": "P2 STUB — Approve path.\n\nImplement in P2:\n1. Route to Platform Router (LinkedIn vs Substack)\n2. LinkedIn path: POST to LinkedIn API with OAuth 2.0\n3. Substack path: POST to Substack API or webhook\n4. Log deployment result\n5. Callback to approval UI with deploy URL\n\nRequires: LinkedIn OAuth 2.0 credentials, Substack API token"
