      "notes": "P2 STUB — Edit path.\n\nImplement in P2:\n1. Take edited_content from request body\n2. Optionally re-run through Voice Engine for consistency check\n3. Return edited content back to approval UI for re-review\n4. Or send directly to platform if auto-approve is enabled\n\nNo external credentials required for the re-route; Anthropic API Key needed if re-running through Voice Engine."
